goalless draw by Shandong Taishan, Yunnan Hongta played to a 1-1
draw with Sichuan Quanxing, Xiamen Xiaxin lost to Chongqing
Longxin 0-3, Qingdao Hainiu and Tianjin Taida drew at 1-1.
