technical content of anti-desertification engineering projects,
improve the quality of these projects, and ensure a satisfactory
environmental impact.
</P>
<P>
More Polluting Firms in China Meet Discharge Standards
</P>
<P>
Eighty-five percent of China's polluting firms had met the
official pollutant discharge requirements by the end of April this
year thanks to a five-year campaign to curb industrial pollution.
</P>
