<HEADLINE> Conference of CAS and CAE to Open in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 4 (Xinhua) -- More than 1,000 academicians are
going to attend the conference of the Chinese Academy of Sciences
(CAS) and the Chinese Academy of Engineering (CAE) which will open
in Beijing tomorrow.
</P>
<P>
It is the most important meeting for the Chinese scientific
circle at the turn of the century. Scientists will offer
suggestions on scientific and economic development to the country'
s decision-makers and will discuss the subjects with their peers.
</P>
<P>
During the five-day conference, heads of the various divisions
of the CAS will give speeches on the strategic development of
their scientific fields. Symposiums on scientific achievements and
development trends will be held.
</P>
<P>
The two academies will elect new foreign academicians and the
CAS will revise its system for selecting academicians.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese Academy of Sciences, which was founded in 1949, has
more than 600 academicians and more than 120 research institutes.
It is the country's most prestigious organization for scientific
and technological research and development.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese Academy of Engineering, founded in 1994, has more
than 500 academicians. 
</P>
</TEXT>
