<HEADLINE> Chinese Premier Calls for Global Cooperation in Environmental Protection (4) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"We must earnestly implement our sustainable development
strategy and put greater efforts to environmental protection and
ecological construction," Zhu said.
</P>
<P>
China will rely on science and technology and increase
investment for conserving water and soil, curbing environmental
pollution, and improving the country's ecological environment
through efforts to plant more trees and grass under a national
overall plan.
</P>
<P>
"We believe through the hard work and unremitting efforts of
the Chinese people, the rivers and lakes across China will become
more clean, the sky more clear and the landscape in the country
more beautiful", the premier said.
</P>
<P>
He also promised that the Chinese government will continue to
adhere to the principles concerning international environmental
cooperation, actively join the international community to solve
global environmental problems, and carry out related international
environmental conventions so as to make due contributions to
protecting the global environment.  
