called for global efforts to fight against the serious pollution
problems and ecological deterioration facing the entire mankind.
</P>
<P>
It is the common aspiration of the people of all nations for a
better environment and a better future, and a historic call for
coordination between global environmental protection and economic
development, Zhu said.
</P>
<P>
